GREAT HORNED DRAGON

The Great Horned Dragon is the apex of playable dragon races.  Ancient and
magnificent, they possess both fire breath AND acid breath, mastery of all
psionic categories, powerful innate magic, and physical attributes that dwarf
most of Rifts Earth's threats.  They are living weapons that predate the
coming of the Rifts by centuries.

ATTRIBUTES (approximate ranges):
  IQ: 18-33  ME: 17-32  MA: 15-30  PS: 36-66 (Supernatural)
  PP: 12-32  PE: 30-55  PB: 6-21   Spd: 14-34

DAMAGE POOL:
  MDC: 6d6 x10 + 100 (approx 160-460 MDC)
  HP: PE + 2d6 (inner life force)

SPECIAL ABILITIES:
  - MDC body: immune to SDC/HP weapons
  - Supernatural Physical Strength and Endurance (extreme values)
  - Fire breath AND acid breath weapons
  - Natural flight
  - Nightvision 300 ft
  - Master psionic: access to all psionic categories
  - Innate magic ability
  - Sense Rifts and ley lines
  - Starting PPE: approximately 200+

PENALTIES:
  - Not OCC eligible
  - Dragon-sized: cannot enter most buildings
  - Primary target of every dragon-hunting faction
  - Cannot use standard equipment

OCC ELIGIBLE: No.
ALIGNMENT: Any.

